N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 20, ch. III, subch. B - Petroleum Business Tax

State Regulations

Part 450 - Petroleum Business Bond Or Other Security (ยง 450.1 to 450.2)

Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 20, ch. III, subch. B
Part 450 contained in this Subchapter was renumbered as part
of a reorganization of the Department's regulations. This Part was previously

Part 63. The rulemaking which renumbered this Part did not make substantive
changes and did not seek to incorporate intervening changes in the law. The
regulations should be read in conjunction with current
law. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
